==English==

===Etymology===

1935, [[American English]]; from ''[[icky-boo]]'' (circa 1920): [[sickly]], [[nauseated]]; [[baby-talk]] corruption of '''[[sick]]'''; from a sentimental term for [[Jazz]] music.

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪki|-ɪki]]

